text: Ahale kitabaka manisaharumadhye uniharusita yud'dha gara, jo allahamathi ra antima dinamathi astha rakhdainan. Ani allaha ra usako rasulale avaidha thahara'eka kurala'i avaidha thahara'umdainan ra nata satya dharmako anupalana gardachan, jabasam'maki parajita bha'i tiniharule jijaya (suraksakara) tirdainan
